===Greeting===
'''Срећан Божић'''
# [[Merry Christmas]]
*:''Usage note:  This greeting is rarely heard in Serbian language and it literally means ''Happy/Merry Christmas''.  However, the more common greeting is [[Христос се роди#Serbian|Христос се роди]].''
